{"tid":2512442,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴選2020-21賽季四大聯賽TOP 5中鋒(排名分先後)","createTime":"2021-05-01T17:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T23:15:27.000Z","uid":199081,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"64b831def3db4f399dcdae64fc5535b17f9e7d4a","tid":2512442,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T17:18:54.000Z","msg":"5. 羅美路盧卡古<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWkon7q5aobymdUUfjzxepy968DiN96n1hWFdgLgWoUbD?filename=V9poVVV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV9poVVV.jpg&h=cbf6048c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n帶領國米排意甲榜首<br />\n自稱top 5俾人笑但的確當之無愧<br />\n<br />\n4. 基斯坦奴朗拿度<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb2DqL4z4QcQzZTF3JHAhKA5EV5M8sSv9GFwVpc823LF3?filename=2SruRu1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2SruRu1.jpg&h=a2f00da8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n表現回落<br />\n但依然排緊意甲射手榜第一<br />\n歐聯柒住出局但無阻佢上榜<br />\n<br />\n3. 夏里瓊<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNcxDqY7R3NzPREJqMr5DwGujaDZmEzvRpbsHbb1xuj2Q?filename=tkhNDaR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtkhNDaR.jpg&h=2e6d03e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英超射手榜助攻榜第一<br />\n俾摩佬調教完由普通一線變做準球王級<br />\n應該好大機會拎埋PFA<br />\n<br />\n2. 羅拔利雲度夫斯基<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPbHXbd5o3o2QWstyvxfddyxKojNyf7dPkbKr13QAa3Do?filename=tjoMTK5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtjoMTK5.jpg&h=f4de759e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n踢完國際賽傷咗成個幾月<br />\n但德甲射手榜仲係以36球拋離緊第二嘅賀蘭<br />\n菠健樂吹奏嘅進波無停完全唔係嗰皮<br />\n<br />\n1. 卡廉賓些馬<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXSWq3FU2V6Hk6UHUL3PcAx158wYTRSBhNFgnSXGJG6dY?filename=mkN2r6Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmkN2r6Z.jpg&h=4586bb97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n皇馬嘅入球之柱<br />\n40%嘅隊內入球佔比<br />\n拋離隊內第二嘅卡些美羅16球<br />\n更加包攬晒今季普斯卡斯獎三甲<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n嚴選2020-21賽季普斯卡斯獎得獎入球<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2508124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2508124</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n今年好有可能繼2013牙朗後<br />\n再次完成「雞胸金球」嘅奇蹟<br />\n佢係本季第一神鋒我相信冇人反對"},{"pid":"a551d65a9a2c6879b86b795e59b698d9606c47db","tid":2512442,"uid":73381,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T17:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZMDD5tsn7BzrgvUnSjjyJSec7Pw1Jof5FiUZzdWCiqk2?filename=OSOpFu9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOSOpFu9.jpg&h=f9146f39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9ebf0a52977192f3172f6ce8863dda6e426c869","tid":2512442,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a551d65a9a2c6879b86b795e59b698d9606c47db","tid":2512442,"uid":73381,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T17:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OSOpFu9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOSOpFu9.jpg&h=f9146f39&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T17:22:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee40dd15dd4a027f52dce504e3d2e2e7f88c618","tid":2512442,"uid":24927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T17:23:48.000Z","msg":"又吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b6ea72ef8d1c582749e2d2fad4116b8ce71f39","tid":2512442,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eee40dd15dd4a027f52dce504e3d2e2e7f88c618","tid":2512442,"uid":24927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T17:23:48.000Z","msg":"又吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T17:25:26.000Z","msg":"認真嚴選"},{"pid":"b510dc6cfba1de7e1a19f8be65000e7dc9